Never Do this
            db.collection.findOne({_id:"efesesffsgrf2325sdefwe"},(err,res)=>{});
    It will return null

    Use it rather
        db.collection.findOne({_id:ObjectId("efesesffsgrf2325sdefwe")})
        It will show the relevant result

When using avatar we see that type of avatar is Buffer in db
To access that buffer string in html,  we need to write like this

<img src="data:image/jpg;base64, <buffer-string> " />


for Sending Email
We use " Send Grid "

